cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a technique for propagating information forward through video data, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a neural network (cs.LG) that processes video frames in an adaptive manner, which is a common approach in deep learning for computer vision tasks. The paper also mentions the use of semantic labels (cs.AI) and video object segmentation (cs.MM), which are specific applications of the proposed technique. Finally, the paper presents experiments that show increased performance compared to previous methods, which is a common evaluation metric in neural network research (cs.NE).
